The data provided are in .zip files that are generally around 50 MB.  Although available to all, the data provided may be of particular value to weather professionals and students of meteorological sciences.  An instructional manual is provided on how to build and develop a basic severe weather report GIS database in ArcGis and is located at the technical documentation site contained in this metadata
